@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false

skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    BorderColor #1565C0
    DiamondBackgroundColor #FFF3E0
    DiamondBorderColor #E65100
}

title Installation Lifecycle Stages

|#E8F5E9| Pre-Installation |
start
:Verify prerequisites;
note right: Check disk space,\npermissions, dependencies
:Resolve dependencies;
:Create directories;

|#E3F2FD| Installation |
:Extract/copy files;
note right: Place artifacts in\ntarget locations
:Set permissions;
:Register with system;
note right: Package manager,\nservices, PATH

|#FFF3E0| Post-Installation |
:Generate configs;
note right: First-run setup,\nenvironment detection
:Initialize data;
:Verify installation;

|#F3E5F5| Runtime |
:Create logs/cache;
:Load plugins;
:Update configs;

|#FFEBEE| Update/Upgrade |
:Backup current state;
:Apply changes;
if (Success?) then (yes)
    :Clean up old files;
else (no)
    :Rollback;
    note right: Restore from backup
endif

|#FCE4EC| Uninstallation |
:Remove files;
:Clean registry;
:Preserve user data?;
note right: Optional: keep\nconfig and data
stop

center footer Design Principle: Plan for the complete lifecycle - installation, updates, and removal
@enduml
